column5: I wanted to share a song my daughter and I recorded last week.  The vocals are done by my 9 year old and I recorded the guitar, bass guitar, drums (from a keyboard) and the other sounds.  She doesn't think her voice sounds very good, but I beg to differ!  I'm very proud of her...she's worked hard on her singing.  She allowed me to post the song, but refused to let me shoot a video of her singing! LOL  I didn't arrange this song...it's actually Miley Cyrus' version of the song...  Hope you enjoy!  <object width="420" height="315"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zDADR16U4I0?version=3&hl=en_US"></param><param'>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zDADR16U4I0?version=3&hl=en_US"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zDADR16U4I0?version=3&hl=en_US" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="420" height="315" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>
That was really great Cliff, and Sidney has some real talent!  Merry Christmas to you and yours.
That is so good Cliff Thanks for putting a smile on my face.  Merry Christmas.
That was Excellent! Thanks for sharing.  Regards, Snowball
That was excellent Cliff    Sydney sure got a great voice   Great job you two Thanks for sharing!!! Jacques
Dam i wish i had high speed , but i should have the download by morning , can't wait ....
Amazing - simply amazing!!!  The talent in that family never ends.  A very Merry Christmas to you and your daughter.   Tracker (Don)
Thanks everyone!  She listened to it this morning and said "I still can't believe that's just you and me doing all that!".  I'm sure we'll do more recordings in the future

Cliff, that was absolutly beautiful!!!!! Ask Sydney if she'll let you do a video of her singing it for Sue and Cliff, we'd love to have it. We are so very proud of her.  BTW, could you post a link to some of the Christmas ones you did in the past, we loved listening to them but when our computer crashed last year I lost all the links.
WOW!!!! that just kick started my Christmas season....absolutly adorable and talented...Thanks for that Sydney...Merry Christmas to you and yours Cliff
Sums it up perfectly, what a great audio memory you can revisit for years to come
Absolutely terrific---you sure have a l'il Angel there  Congrats
Thank you everyone!!      Cliff...I asked her about the video...she said "I'll think about it!".  That's more than I got! LOL

Thanks for sharing! Love your guitar tone. Her singing is good - way better than mine, haha!  My wife and I shoulda did another Christmas song this year... Argh. There's still time... I'll think on it.
